{"tid":212971,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎講下你初戀","createTime":"2017-04-22T20:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T20:59:22.000Z","uid":84911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"204f5ec7a579cc70465e19ec581529a570b99756","tid":212971,"uid":84911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T20:02:44.000Z","msg":"初戀係中四 話細唔細話大唔大<br />\n但個陣都仲on99咁 條條fing<br />\n第一次拍拖咩都唔識 <br />\n淨係識wtsapp瘋狂sd心心比條女 <br />\n簡簡單單互相flirt下又過一日<br />\n就係因為咁 條女覺得我唔識拍拖<br />\n口花花咁 比唔到安全感佢<br />\n我個陣諗野又on99 思想唔成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點應對好 就無疾而終左<br />\n<br />\n後來拍過幾次拖 慢慢學識點為之拍拖<br />\n點為之對個女仔好 <br />\n但已經冇左個種好緬典既感覺 <br />\n突然間好掛住初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好想比佢睇下宜家改變左既我 <br />\n重新再黎多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n錯的時間 對的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c44f099b0ddc8472043e1929a6b6188805eb6e1","tid":212971,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T20:08:34.000Z","msg":"覺得初戀唔係自己嘅初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時咁啱身邊人拍晒拖佢又咁啱鐘意我<br />\n自己又想試下拍拖先同左佢一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後拍左兩個月同佢講冇feel 分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人認為第二次算得上係自己嘅初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係因為鍾意佢而一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e09860683212a3050ceb8902deef7d08350fcec","tid":212971,"uid":18955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T20:10:39.000Z","msg":"初戀 = 第一個女朋友 = 第一次比左佢 = 第一個老婆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4773679f8d4b272674d499316db3374fccf79f10","tid":212971,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T20:12:15